[size=6]DESCRIPTION[/size]

[size=3]Simple warpaint textures for female.KANJI is Japanese character.
They character have unfathomable meanings.
Resolution is 2K.[/size]

[size=6]LIST(v1)[/size]

[size=5]一二三四五六七八九十
闇威印雨影音夏火海楽
喝漢喜弓京空月好嫌拳
紅高魂最桜殺山燦斬侍
始終字疾狩暑女心森真
神吹水是生蒼赤泉禅創
創蒼男知地恥智蝶怒盗
灯道乳忍破曝罰妃緋飛
風淵碧望無鳴夜葉来雷
理竜力林涙冷恋和澪絆[/size]

[size=6]LIST(v2)[/size]

[size=5]悪隠格鬼古光骨戦争虫
討肉爆悲母[/size]

[size=6]REQUIREMENT MODS[/size]

[size=3]SKSE
////////////////////////////////
Please type SKSE.ini.
[Display]
iTintTextureResolution=2048
///////////////////////////////[/size]

[size=6]HOW TO USE[/size]

[size=3]1.Extraction.
2.Copy to Your Data/textures/actors/character/character assets/tintmasks.
3.Rename to femaleheadwarpaint_01-10.
4.Read.[/size]
